<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.4.1/css/bootstrap.min.css">
  <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/3.5.1/jquery.min.js"></script>
  <script src="https://maxcdn.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/3.4.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
  <title>Edit Profile - Gainen</title>
</head>

<body>
  <header>
    <%- include('layouts/navbar') -%>
    <h2>Edit User Profile</h2>
  </header>
  
  <main>

  <form name="deleteProfile" action="" method="POST">

    Are you sure you want to delete your profile, <%= username %>?<br>

    This is an awesome platform to fund your ideas, but still if you would like to delete your profile 
    we assure you that the following details would be deleted from our database:<br>

    First Name: <%= firstName %><br>
    Last Name: <%= lastName %><br>
    Email Id: <%= emailId %><br>
    Phone Number: <%= phone %><br>
    Profile Pic:
    <img src="/profile_pics/<%= profilePicName %>" alt="User Profile Pic" width="100" height="100">
        
    <button type="submit">Delete Profile</button>


  </form>

  </main>
</body>

<%- include('layouts/footer') -%>

</html>